item.title: Options Panel
item.dc:creator: paulo
item.content:encoded:
ImpulsePress Premium provides a powerful options panel that you can use to configure your theme. This framework is easily extendable so that you can easily add options to your theme. [row class="row"] [col class="col-xs-4"]

General Options

In the general options tab, you can configure the logo of your login window, your favicon and to eanble or disable breadcrumbs for your whole site. [/col] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Header Options

In the header options section, you can configure whether the navbar is fixed, your website logo, enable or disable the search bar and social icons on your top navigation bar. [/col] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Footer Options

Similarly to the header options, you can enable or disable the displaying of the social icons on your footer. You can also add a custom Copyright and "Powered By" text. [/col] [/row] [row class="row"] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Styling

Impulse Press allows you to customize the look and feel of your theme completely. You can either use the many options for text colors, links, buttons, navigation, etc, or you can include your own CSS theme in a directory. [/col] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Typography

In this area, you can configure the font styles and sizes. We support plenty of Google Fonts. [/col] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Blog

In the blog options, you can choose to display the blog metadata or not. You can also customize the text of the "read more" button. [/col] [/row] [row class="row"] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Social

In this section, you can configure the links to various social media accounts. [/col] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Tracking

Here you can enter your custom tracking code for Google Analytics for example. [/col] [col class="col-xs-4"]

Options Backup

This feature allows you to backup your options to a file. [/col] [/row]

item.title: Impulse Press 1.3 Released
item.dc:creator: paulo
item.content:encoded: We've  just released Impulse Press 1.3! In this version: * Many bug fixes in the options panel * Added all bootstrap buttons options panel page * Introduced Custom Meta Boxes - This feature allows you to add meta boxes to your pages. * Enhanced Home Parallax page - Using the metaboxes, the parallax page template is now configurable for background images and parallax speed. * Breadcrumbs are now optional per page * Possibility to disable styling options and use CSS instead - This is a big thing. Theme developers who prefer working with CSS are now able to disable the styling options. Impulse Press is available for download here.
